config BR2_PACKAGE_BOND
	bool "bond"
	select BR2_PACKAGE_MESSAGE_GENERATION
	select BR2_PACKAGE_STD_MSGS
	help
	  bond package: a bond allows two processes, A and B, to know
	  when the other has terminated, either cleanly or by
	  crashing. The bond remains connected until it is either
	  broken explicitly or until a heartbeat times out.

	  http://wiki.ros.org/bond
